{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/social-situations/care-givers-allowance","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Care-giver’s allowance","meta_description":"Compensation for self-employed and care-giver allowance for employees/ DPP/ DPČ ","content":{"processed":"<h2>Care-giver’s allowance</h2>\n<p>We provide more information regarding this issue in the area of ​​compensation.</p>\n<p>You can find out more about the <a href=\"/situace/kompenzace/krizove-osetrovne\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Krizové ošetřovné\">crisis nursing allowance</a> and also about the entitlement to nursing allowance if you belong to the group of <a href=\"/node/282\" rel=\"nofollow\">self-employed persons</a>, or if you are an <a href=\"/node/282\" rel=\"nofollow\">employee</a>, or <a href=\"/node/282\" rel=\"nofollow\">working at DPP or DPČ</a>.</p>\n<p>Are you looking for information about \"Izolačka\" (a contribution for a time spend in quarantine) - a contribution in addition to sick leave? You will find information about her in the life situation <a href=\"/situace/zamestnani/nahrada-mzdy\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Náhrada mzdy\">Wage compensation</a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/social-situations/care-givers-allowance"},"changed":"2021-03-06T17:23:13+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2021-01-03T00:50:27+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia","drupal_internal__tid":"33"}],"icon":{"code":"card_giftcard"},"situation_type":{"name":"Social situations","path":{"alias":"/situations/social-situations"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"people_alt"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Compensation - business","path":{"alias":"/situations/business-activities/compensation-business","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Caregiver’s allowance for full-time employees/people with work agreements","path":{"alias":"/situations/compensati